{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"toolu_01CbGTxu7PoEWH38vrBzspti","type":"tool_result","content":"commit dc3715d718ecb39e7569c97f254501d5f257c636\nAuthor: Lee Gonzales <lee.gonzales@gmail.com>\nDate:   Fri Mar 20 11:00:05 2026 -0600\n\n    feat: add AUX block support for auxiliary content drawer\n    \n    Add a new <!-- AUX title=\"...\" --> block type to PK v5 talk tracks that\n    renders as a slide-over drawer with copy-to-clipboard. Designed for\n    prompts, handouts, and reference text that participants need to copy\n    but should not be read aloud.\n    \n    Parser changes:\n    - New AuxContent type (title + body) on SlideContent\n    - Regex extraction of AUX blocks alongside existing AUDIO blocks\n    - Zero or one AUX block per slide; null if absent\n    \n    HTML renderer (standard + standalone):\n    - Pill button in bottom-left corner on slides with AUX content\n    - Slide-over drawer (40% width) from right with markdown rendering\n    - Copy-to-clipboard (raw markdown, not HTML)\n    - Escape key and backdrop click dismissal\n    - Responsive (full-width on mobile)\n    - CSS matches existing PK dark theme palette\n    \n    18 new tests covering parsing, rendering, and edge cases.\n    All 206 tests pass, including 188 pre-existing.\n    \n    Co-Authored-By: Claude Opus 4.6 (1M context) <noreply@anthropic.com>\n\n src/parsers/index.ts                   |   1 +\n src/parsers/talk-track.ts              |  37 +++\n src/parsers/types.ts                   |  13 +\n src/renderers/html/index.ts            |   1 +\n src/renderers/html/standalone.ts       | 199 +++++++++++++-\n src/renderers/html/template.ts         | 466 ++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++-\n src/renderers/html/types.ts            |  13 +\n tests/aux-block.test.ts                | 243 +++++++++++++++++\n tests/fixtures/aux-block-talk-track.md |  79 ++++++\n 9 files changed, 1047 insertions(+), 5 deletions(-)","is_error":false}]},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"